{"tid":1494611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去到一個地步，五大訴求會結合成一個訴求","createTime":"2019-08-21T16:55:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T05:58:20.000Z","uid":222614,"like":69,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"6a562728115e16115fb9d9290c5b8fe2263db43c","tid":1494611,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"如果政府係<span style=\"color: red;\">823死線</span>之後仍然態度強硬<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求將<span style=\"color: red;\">不復存在</span>，因為已經無可能再畀機會政府作任何回應<br />\n<br />\n換黎既，係宣告<span style=\"color: red;\">「一國兩制」徹底失敗</span><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求會結合成一個訴求：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">成立新政府</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">到時所有香港人都有義務去為新政府既誕生出一分力！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢個係畀現屆香港政府既最後警告：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">立即滿足五大訴求，否則後果自負！</span></span>"},{"pid":"94d1de1c0b363c4f1f4dc4981bd1272226184122","tid":1494611,"uid":222614,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:56:04.000Z","msg":"立即滿足五大訴求，否則後果自負！"},{"pid":"52c7f26b844d08ee5b458eedd850a92ea90cf38c","tid":1494611,"uid":48881,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"新政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec82a6b9cc5f1ceaf220651565f46d628ba676fc","tid":1494611,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:56:22.000Z","msg":"立即滿足五大訴求，否則後果自負！"},{"pid":"9914976f9b32ae0b4c2d9102dcf39628c87dd755","tid":1494611,"uid":245552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:57:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm